{"tid":511481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TNG電子錢包進攻的士　將延伸至小巴","createTime":"2017-12-27T14:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T18:04:37.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9824a3a667d8440523c506619998041c8efef8e5","tid":511481,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1415000/1416972/KakaoTalk_2016042_191528675_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1415000%2F1416972%2FKakaoTalk_2016042_191528675_1024.jpg&h=ff187a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTNG日前擴展服務至的士，其行政總裁江慶恩透露，下一步將延伸至小巴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTNG電子錢包日前擴展至的士，用戶可用App作實時付款，司機在翌日可於銀行戶口收款；該公司透露，下一步會將服務延伸至小巴，並計劃於6月底前新增轉帳服務，將TNG戶口內金額轉帳至銀行戶口。<br />\n<br />\nTNG創辦人兼行政總裁江慶恩指出，合共有2000架的士之新興車行及順安車行已答應參與，初步已有數百架的士登記，冀望最終全港有約1.8萬架的士均會使用。<br />\n<br />\n用戶登上支援TNG的士，在前座後枕貼有司機的QR碼，付款時只要用TNG App掃瞄QR碼，輸入車資及交易密碼完成。司機實時收到款項於TNG戶口中，翌日可轉帳到指定銀行戶口；每位司機新開帳戶可獲贈100元，每日每支旗可獲1元津貼，上限15元。江慶恩指，若乘客少付車資，司機收到實時通知可即時「追數」；若多付車資，司機亦可實時轉帳給客戶。他預料，年內補貼2,000萬元，但沒有設補貼上限。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，TNG將擴展至小巴，屆時車廂內有裝置，用戶不用輸入密碼付款，但拒絕透露詳情，指正待運輸處審批申請，他又透露，兩至三個月後，新增多1000個零售點，全為連鎖食肆，同時亦計劃於6月底前，可將TNG帳戶金額，轉帳至全港各銀行。<br />\n<br />\nTNG去年11月伙拍759阿信屋推出電子支付，曾吸引港人瘋狂下載，TNG目前已有30萬活躍用戶，二月份每日增值人數達2.8萬，增值金額平均為145元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1415000/1416972/KakaoTalk_20160428_191527137_1024.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1415000%2F1416972%2FKakaoTalk_20160428_191527137_1024.jpg&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b5db036e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1415000/1416972/KakaoTalk_20160428_191527137_1024.jpg</a><br />\n用戶只須於TNG App內掃瞄車廂內的QR CODE，並輸入密碼及車資來完成交易。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1416972/TNG%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%E9%80%B2%E6%94%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E3%80%80%E5%B0%87%E5%BB%B6%E4%BC%B8%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1416972%2FTNG%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%258C%2585%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a2797a84\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1416972/TNG%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%E9%80%B2%E6%94%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E3%80%80%E5%B0%87%E5%BB%B6%E4%BC%B8%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4</a>"},{"pid":"768c3d47e26c17c3f1eedb4c09d8a9008ff11292","tid":511481,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"又QR CODE"},{"pid":"7a26e22a3ed89adbd1f6f32557076cab5ede8baf","tid":511481,"uid":36964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我要Apple Pay/Android Pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91244fe54b98dca05a70b52aae44d737c7d9b551","tid":511481,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dccc2799bf429123af0ae3ad6e0f68caeda51581","tid":511481,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a26e22a3ed89adbd1f6f32557076cab5ede8baf","tid":511481,"uid":36964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我要Apple Pay/Android Pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec9b0e9208c71033d7de2bf26d2857f6174d078","tid":511481,"uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":0